description: frank. gourmet hot dogs and sausages offers quality, locally sourced, from scratch ingredients. With twists on popular favorites like the bahn-mi, or a frank topped with chipotle lobster mac n cheese, there's a frank for everyone. Frank. also offers hand cut potato and sweet potato chips, deep fried "truck made" pickles, and a rotating gelato flavor from grateful spoon.This great truck was started by Philly transplant Adam, who was tickled by the idea of being able to top a hot dog with just about anything. This shows up quite readily in his work, as he offers dogs topped with everything from aioli to funyuns. Read more about this great truck and its delicious dogs on the Roaming Hunger blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/8285/top-that
